## Creative Flying

---


[Entity Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/entity_condition_types/creative_flying)

Checks if the player is Creative Mode flying.

Type ID: `origins:creative_flying`

---

### Examples
```json
"condition": {
    "type": "origins:creative_flying"
}
```
